      "EnemyBuffAVictoriaRegularBoss": {
        "id": "EnemyBuffAVictoriaRegularBoss",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Spreading Chill",
          "description": "Allies gain 2 Spirit for each non-sleeping enemy on the battlefield.\n\nThen a random enemy has their Burn removed, and is granted Frostburn and infected with it. This skill becomes locked for 50TU after use. Usable 5 times per battle.\n\nAfter the end of each turn, this infection will trigger to apply Frostburn to a random non-Frostburned unit on the infected unit's team. Infection ends after 3 triggers (even if they find no valid target) or once the infected enemy is defeated or leaves the battlefield. Infection is not a status effect and cannot be prevented or purified, but the effect spread by the infection may be. A unit cannot get a new infection until their existing one ends.\n\nWhen a unit has Frostburn and they get the turn, they will lose the turn as if they were sleeping, then Frostburn is removed and that unit is granted the Burn status effect. Frostburn is not a status effect, but effects that remove negative status effects will also remove Frostburn. Frostburn will end if the affected unit is defeated or leaves the battlefield. Frostburn cannot apply to boss units, and cannot stack. Burn will overwrite other status effects. Any unit that deals damage to or is dealt damage by a unit with burn will also become burned.",
          "selected": "May Gain Spirit, Grants Frostburn & Infection"
        },
